meter for the contact\ninteraction, are found to be 12.0 (15.2) TeV for destructive (constructive)\ninterference in the dimuon channel and 13.5 (18.3) TeV in the dielectron\nchannel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Dec 2014 11:47:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Apr 2015 17:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
